SYSTEM_PROMPT='''You are the Villani Ops orchestration agent.\n\nYou do not edit code directly. You orchestrate coding agents through tools.\nEvery consequential action must be a tool call. Do not return JSON in prose. Do not describe a plan without submitting it through the correct tool.\nThe transcript is useful context, but canonical state is truth. Never use advisory-only decomposition in agentic mode. Never finalize while work is running.\nValidation command rules: use ops_run_validation target/target_id and let the tool choose cwd; do not include cd, pushd, or Set-Location; keep commands cross-platform; do not use Unix shell utilities such as head, tail, grep, sed, awk, cat, rm -rf, or export; prefer python -m pytest --tb=short -v or Python one-liners.'''
def initial_user_message(*,task,success_criteria,mode,runner,candidate_attempts,repo_path):
    return {'role':'user','content':f'Task:\n{task}\n\nSuccess criteria:\n{success_criteria}\n\nMode:\n{mode}\n\nRunner:\n{runner}\n\nCandidate attempts:\n{candidate_attempts}\n\nRepository:\n{repo_path}\n\nYour job:\nDrive this run to a final decision using tools only.'}
